  Locus:
    Page: 110
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Dreams
---
Dream lofty dreams, and as you dream, so shall you become. Your Vision is
the promise of what you shall one day be, your Ideal is the prophecy of what
you shall at last unveil.
